---

<SiteLayout
  title="Residential Dryer Vent Cleaning & Repair in Central Florida"
  description="Certified residential dryer vent cleaning and repair services in Central Florida focused on fire prevention, safer dryer operation, and efficient airflow."
  imageUrl={heroImageUrl}
  overlayHeader={true}
>
  <HeroSection
    align="left-bottom"
    imageUrl={heroImageUrl}
    topper="Residential Service"
    title="Residential Dryer Duct Cleaning / Repair"
    body="At Hygienic Air, Inc, we prioritize fire safety and recognize the critical importance of annual dryer duct cleanings and inspections. Our team boasts more Certified CSIA Dryer Duct Technicians than any other company in Central Florida. With state-of-the-art equipment and extensive knowledge, you can rest assured that your home's dryer duct will remain clear of obstructions. Additionally, we are proud members of the National Fire Protection Agency (NFPA), further demonstration our dedication to safety and compliance."
    actions={[
      { href: "tel:+13528012788", label: "Call Us", variant: "primary" },
      {
        href: "https://client.housecallpro.com/customer_portal/request-link?token=e189962ac4d546e3b9e813944ff69b3c",
        label: "Book Online",
        variant: "secondary",
        external: true,
      },
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section section--alert">
    <div class="u-container">
      <article class="notice-box alert-box">
        <h3>ATTENTION</h3>
        <p>
          IRC M1502.3 states that screens on dryer vent terminations are a violation and fire
          hazard. These screens are often left in place during roofing work and should be removed
          and corrected.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--page-intro">
    <div class="u-container">
      <header class="section__head section__head--left content-stack">
        <p class="section-topper">Clean Duct, Clean Home Air</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Annual Dryer Vent Cleaning Is a Home Safety Essential</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="split-grid content-grid">
        <div class="rich-text">
          <p>
            Cleaning frequency: every year. Annual cleaning helps reduce lint accumulation,
            protects airflow, and lowers avoidable dryer fire risks.
          </p>
          <p>
            Clogged or screened terminations can lead to longer dry times, equipment failures, and
            severe safety risks. We can dispatch a certified dryer vent technician to bring your
            system back to safer operation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="notice-box">
          <h3>Warning Signs It's Time To Clean</h3>
          <ul class="check-list">
            {warningSigns.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--deep-blue">
    <div class="u-container">
      <header class="section__head content-stack">
        <p class="section-topper">Dryer Fire Facts</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Did You Know Dryer Fires In The U.S. Annually Cause</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="metric-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));">
